9, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"George allegedly taunted the woman as he shoved a towel down her throat and choked her, according to police.\", \"from\": 1470, \"to\": 1578, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"George also mocked her for praying to God, saying that she would not die during one of his multiple attacks, the reports added.\", \"from\": 1579, \"to\": 1706, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"The abuse began in September 2023 and only ended last month, police said.\", \"from\": 1708, \"to\": 1781, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"The restauranteur turned himself in on Friday after a warrant was issued for his arrest on charges of attempted murder, rape, felony assault, four counts of kidnapping and two counts of strangulation.\", \"from\": 1783, \"to\": 1983, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"George was released on a $200,000 bond Tuesday after appearing in Cleveland Municipal Court.\", \"from\": 1985, \"to\": 2077, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2051, \"end\": 2060, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Cleveland_Brown\", \"score\": 0.9999999998663043, \"rank\": 1.3406263819460001e-10, \"text\": \"Cleveland\", \"types\": [\"Q95074\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Cleveland_Brown\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Cleveland_Brown\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"In a protection order, the judge barred George from contacting his alleged victim.\", \"from\": 2078, \"to\": 2160, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"The woman \\\"fears for her life,\\\" according to court documents.\", \"from\": 2162, \"to\": 2223, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"In the first attack detailed by police, George allegedly threw his victim into a kitchen cabinet so hard that the glass shattered.\", \"from\": 2225, \"to\": 2355, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"The next month, George pinned her to the floor, choked her and slammed her head into a table repeatedly.\", \"from\": 2357, \"to\": 2461, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Police say she suffered blurred vision and bleeding and ringing in her ears afterwards.\", \"from\": 2462, \"to\": 2549, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"The defendant then had victim treated by his business'(s) nurse-practitioner who diagnosed her with post-concussion syndrome,\\\" according to a report by the Cleveland police Domestic Violence Unit contained in the arrest warrant.\", \"from\": 2551, \"to\": 2780, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2708, \"end\": 2717, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Cleveland_Brown\", \"score\": 0.9999999998663043, \"rank\": 1.3406263819460001e-10, \"text\": \"Cleveland\", \"types\": [\"Q95074\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Cleveland_Brown\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Cleveland_Brown\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"George is accused of shoving a gun in the woman's stomach after she tried to flee his home, of raping her after she exited a shower, and of choking her on multiple occasions.\", \"from\": 2782, \"to\": 2956, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"Defendant pulled her hair, strangled her and threw her all over the house,\\\" a Cleveland police detective wrote.\", \"from\": 2958, \"to\": 3070, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3037, \"end\": 3046, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Cleveland_Brown\", \"score\": 0.9999999998663043, \"rank\": 1.3406263819460001e-10, \"text\": \"Cleveland\", \"types\": [\"Q95074\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Cleveland_Brown\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Cleveland_Brown\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"George's attorney, Kevin Spellacy, denied the allegations.\", \"from\": 3072, \"to\": 3130, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Greg Owenwrites about politics and culture for LGBTQ Nation.\", \"from\": 3132, \"to\": 3192, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3179, \"end\": 3191, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/LGBTQ_Nation\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"LGBTQ Nation\", \"types\": [\"Q386724\"], \"wikid\":